  "extraHighlightWords": [],
  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "My aunt employed a professional photographer for a pre-wedding photo shoot, and the whole family was invited, whether we wanted to pose or not.",
      "zh": "我姑姑請了一位專業攝影師來拍婚紗照，全家人都被邀請入鏡，不管我們想不想擺姿勢。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The shoot started at three pm sharp at a garden studio, chosen mainly because it was convenient for both families to reach.",
      "zh": "拍攝下午三點整在一間花園攝影棚準時開始，選這裡主要是因為對雙方家庭來說都很方便。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The photographer explained one basic principle right away: relax your shoulders, or the camera lens sees every bit of tension.",
      "zh": "攝影師一開始就解釋了一個基本原則：放鬆肩膀，否則鏡頭會拍出每一絲緊繃。"
    },
    {
      "en": "He used his latest camera, which had a feature that took ten photos per second, just in case someone blinked and shut their eyes.",
      "zh": "他用了他最新款的相機，有一個每秒能拍十張的功能，以防有人眨眼閉上眼睛。"
    },
    {
      "en": "My aunt looked genuinely stunning, and even Sophia admitted her beauty that afternoon was hard to put into words.",
      "zh": "我姑姑那天下午真的美極了，連 Sophia 都承認她的美難以用言語形容。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The dress material caught the light beautifully, though my aunt admitted it made walking on the grass slightly harder than expected.",
      "zh": "禮服的布料在光線下美得驚人，不過我姑姑坦承這讓她走在草地上比想像中還難走。"
    },
    {
      "en": "William, one of the youngest kids there, nearly slipped on the wet grass while running toward his future uncle for a photo.",
      "zh": "William 是那裡最小的孩子之一，衝去找他未來的姑丈拍照時差點在濕草地上滑倒。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The photographer patiently tried to teach him to stand still, but William's idea of a \"cute pose\" mostly involved flexing like a tiny superhero.",
      "zh": "攝影師很有耐心地教他站好，但 William 心目中的「可愛姿勢」大多是像個迷你超級英雄一樣秀肌肉。"
    },
    {
      "en": "For one photo, the whole family stood beside a lone tree at the center of the garden, with the sun shining brightly above us.",
      "zh": "有一張照片，全家人站在花園中央一棵孤獨的樹旁，陽光在我們頭上明亮地照著。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The photographer kept switching between a wide shot and a medium shot, saying each angle told a slightly different story about the family.",
      "zh": "攝影師不斷在遠景跟中景之間切換，說每個角度都能講出這個家庭稍微不同的故事。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Bernice, who came along as an honorary family member, forgot she was not actually supposed to be in every single photo, and nobody had the heart to stop her.",
      "zh": "以榮譽家庭成員身份跟來的 Bernice，忘了自己其實不是每一張照片都該入鏡，但沒有人狠得下心阻止她。"
    },
    {
      "en": "My uncle joked that although this was a small photo shoot, it felt like the whole event was, therefore, technically a small production of its own.",
      "zh": "我叔叔開玩笑說，雖然這只是個小小的拍攝，因此嚴格來說整個活動其實也算是它自己的一場小型製作。"
    },
    {
      "en": "By the latter half of the shoot, everyone was a little tired, and even the youths in the family had run out of patience for smiling on command.",
      "zh": "拍攝進行到後半段，大家都有點累了，就連家裡的年輕人也對配合微笑用完了耐心。"
    },
    {
      "en": "The staff serving cold drinks nearby said, based on their experience, most families win the battle against tiredness once snacks appear.",
      "zh": "在旁邊供應冷飲的工作人員說，根據他們的經驗，一旦點心出現，大部分家庭都能贏過疲憊的挑戰。"
    },
    {
      "en": "They were completely right; the moment snacks arrived, every kid, teen, man, and woman in the family suddenly found fresh energy for a few more photos.",
      "zh": "他們說得完全正確；點心一到，家裡不管是小孩、青少年、男人還是女人，突然都又找到力氣多拍幾張照片。"
    },
    {
      "en": "By the end, the photographer said he had captured, without a doubt, one of the most genuinely happy families he had shot all year.",
      "zh": "拍攝結束時，攝影師說毫無疑問，這是他今年拍過最真心快樂的家庭之一。"
    }
  ],
